These are Puzzles for 7x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-1::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: march, june, july
City: paris, venice, hamburg
3 different games are played: chess, mah-jongg, canasta
3 different pets are kept: frog, cat, ferret
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, ritmeester, blend
The people use 3 different means of transport: roller, trike, tram
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: orchid, sunflower, daffodil
 1. the person who growsorchid is the person driving the trike##1
 2. the person who growsdaffodil is the owner of the ferret##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in july is between the person driving the tram and the person who's birthday is in june##2
 4. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
 5. the owner of the cat is the person traveling to hamburg##1
 6. the person playing canasta is the person driving the roller##1
 7. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person traveling to paris##1
 8. the person who growssunflower is on the left of the dunhill-smoker##1
 9. the person who growsorchid is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
10. the person playing mah-jongg is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |
| Birthday      | june    | july   | march           |
| City          | venice       | hamburg    | paris         |
| Game         | mah-jongg    | canasta  | chess        |
| Pet           | frog | cat   | ferret      |
| Cigar   | ritmeester        | blend    | dunhill       |
| Transport   | trike     | roller  | tram       |
| Flower         | orchid     | sunflower | daffodil |

