The people's birthday is in 3 different months: august, june, october
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, cain, havana
3 different games are played: whist, monopoly, billiard
The people have 3 different jobs:  musician, software-developer, project-manager
 1. the person playing billiard is the cain-smoker##1
 2. the person playing billiard is the person who likes pink##1
 3. the person who likes pink is on the right of the person playing whist##1
 4. the musician is between the person who's hobby is filmmaking and the person who's hobby is writing##2
 5. the havana-smoker is on the far left##1
 6. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the person who's birthday is in august##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the project-manager##1
 8. the cape-cod house is the person who likes cape-cod##1
 9. the person who likes pink is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
10. the person playing billiard is on the left of the townhouse house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |       3       |
| Hobby      | writing   | fishing    | filmmaking         |
| House          | cape-cod    | victorian | townhouse          |
| Color   | cape-cod  | pink  | azure     |
