.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-3::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, swisher, siglo
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: march, december, september
House: futuristic, craftsman, townhouse
City: hamburg, new-york, san-francisco
3 different games are played: chess, snooker, whist
There are 3 different favourite beverages: mirinda, coffee, soy-milk
The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, skateboard, helicopter
 1. the swisher-smoker is the person drinking coffee##1
 2. the person playing whist is the person who's birthday is in december##1
 3. the futuristic house is the siglo-smoker##1
 4. the craftsman house is the person drinking coffee##1
 5. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
 6. the craftsman house is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in september is between the person playing snooker and the person traveling to san-francisco##2
 8. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person traveling to hamburg##1
 9. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
10. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the swisher-smoker##1
11. the person playing snooker is the siglo-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |      3       |
| Cigar          | siglo      | swisher      | ritmeester      |
| Birthday         | march   | september | december |
| House   | futuristic | craftsman    | townhouse          |
| City   | new-york       | hamburg      | san-francisco          |
| Game   | snooker    | chess  | whist      |
| Beverage           | mirinda   | coffee  | soy-milk        |
| Transport         | bus  | skateboard   | helicopter     |

