The people's birthday is in 3 different months: june, july, may
The people use 3 different means of transport: trike, bike, roller
There 3 different types of food: lemon, artichoke, garlic
 1. the person eating artichoke is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
 2. the person who's sport is parkour is the person driving the roller##1
 3. the person eating garlic is on the left of the person who likes orange##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in june is between the person who likes turquise and the person who's sport is parkour##2
 6. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the craftsman house##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in june is the wooden house##1
 8. the person traveling to boston is the person eating garlic##1
 9. the person who's sport is surfing is between the person traveling to boston and the person traveling to san-francisco##2
10. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person driving the bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2        |       3       |
| Sport      | parkour | surfing           | ice-hockey      |
| House         | craftsman       | wooden         | townhouse       |
