.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-5::.
There are 3 different nationalities: malaysian, dutch, polish
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: azalea, poppy, daffodil
3 different games are played: bridge, poker, whist
The people have 3 different hobbies: chess, writing, woodworking
There are 3 different favourite colors: ivory, emerald, lilac
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: adventure, romance, superhero
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, chaman, fonseca
 1. the person who growspoppy is on the left of the fonseca-smoker##1
 2. the game-smoker is on the left of the person who likes ivory##1
 3. the polish is the person watching superhero movies##1
 4. the dutch is on the far right##1
 5. the person watching superhero movies is between the person watching romance movies and the person who's hobby is writing##2
 6. the person watching superhero movies is between the person watching adventure movies and the person who likes lilac##2
 7. the game-smoker is between the person who growsdaffodil and the malaysian##2
 8. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
 9. the person playing poker is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
10. the person playing bridge is the person who growsdaffodil##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |       2       |     3      |
| Nationality      | malaysian          | polish         | dutch      |
| Flower          | azalea     | poppy         | daffodil |
| Game           | whist | poker    | bridge   |
| Hobby   | chess        | woodworking          | writing        |
| Color           | lilac        | emerald         | ivory      |
| Movie-Genre         | romance     | superhero | adventure   |
| Cigar     | chaman    | game          | fonseca       |

