.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-17::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: june, september, december
House: cape-cod, cottage, craftsman
City: hannover, liverpool, boston
3 different games are played: billiard, whist, chess
There are 3 different favourite colors: orange, blood-red, black
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, swisher, prince
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: pop, jazz, electronic
 1. the prince-smoker is in the middle##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in september is in the middle##1
 3. the person playing chess is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
 4. the craftsman house is the person traveling to liverpool##1
 5. the fan pop is on the right of the person playing chess##1
 6. the person who likes black is on the left of the person traveling to liverpool##1
 7. the fan electronic is between the person who's birthday is in june and the person playing billiard##2
 8. the person traveling to hannover is on the right of the bongani-smoker##1
 9. the person traveling to liverpool is the fan pop##1
10. the person who likes black is on the left of the person who likes blood-red##1
11. the fan pop is the person playing billiard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |
| Birthday      | june | september      | december      |
| House         | cape-cod     | cottage     | craftsman  |
| City   | boston | hannover  | liverpool |
| Game   | whist  | chess     | billiard |
| Color           | orange        | black | blood-red     |
| Cigar         | bongani    | prince | swisher   |
| Music-Genre     | jazz        | electronic        | pop   |

