.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-18::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: november, may, july
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: iris, zinnia, balloon-flower
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: r&b, hip-hop, indie
There are 3 different nationalities: brazilian, polish, indian
3 different games are played: whist, snooker, go
City: rome, venice, berlin
There are 3 different favourite colors: amber, fuchsia, green
1. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the indian##1
2. the person who likes green is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
3. the person who growszinnia is on the left of the brazilian##1
4. the person traveling to rome is between the person playing whist and the polish##2
5. the person who growsballoon-flower is between the indian and the fan indie##2
6. the fan hip-hop is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
7. the person traveling to venice is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
8. the person who likes amber is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
9. the person playing snooker is on the left of the brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3      |
| Birthday      | november      | may      | july       |
| Flower          | zinnia      | balloon-flower    | iris   |
| Music-Genre         | indie    | r&b     | hip-hop     |
| Nationality           | polish    | brazilian | indian   |
| Game   | snooker    | go    | whist       |
| City         | berlin | rome      | venice    |
| Color     | fuchsia       | amber | green |

