.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-19::.
3 different pets are kept: cat, frog, dog
House: futuristic, wooden, palace
There are 3 different favourite colors: emerald, yellow, lavender
The people have 3 different jobs:  engineer, journalist, bartender
There are 3 different nationalities: thai, colombian, french
3 different games are played: scrabble, snooker, chess
City: san-francisco, paris, new-york
1. the person traveling to paris is the person who likes yellow##1
2. the person playing snooker is on the right of the engineer##1
3. the person playing chess is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
4. the bartender is on the right of the person traveling to new-york##1
5. the wooden house is between the owner of the dog and the person who likes emerald##2
6. the palace house is on the right of the french##1
7. the owner of the cat is on the right of the colombian##1
8. the person traveling to san-francisco is the bartender##1
9. the person who likes emerald is on the right of the person who likes lavender##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |      3       |
| Pet      | dog       | cat     | frog         |
| House          | futuristic     | wooden      | palace     |
| Color         | yellow | lavender    | emerald      |
| Job   | engineer   | journalist | bartender    |
| Nationality   | colombian        | french     | thai   |
| Game         | scrabble     | snooker | chess |
| City     | paris     | new-york       | san-francisco    |

