.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-20::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: d&b, country, salsa
3 different games are played: backgammon, mah-jongg, snooker
The people have 3 different hobbies: photography, sudoku, chess
There are 3 different favourite colors: light-blue, white, brown
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: disaster, comedy, thriller
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, dannemann, blend
House: gothic-revival, tower, victorian
1. the fan d&b is the person playing snooker##1
2. the victorian house is the dunhill-smoker##1
3. the person who's hobby is photography is between the fan salsa and the person watching thriller movies##2
4. the person who likes light-blue is on the left of the victorian house##1
5. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the blend-smoker##1
6. the tower house is on the left of the victorian house##1
7. the person who's hobby is sudoku is the person playing backgammon##1
8. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
9. the person who likes white is between the person playing backgammon and the gothic-revival house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| Music-Genre      | country    | d&b       | salsa      |
| Game          | backgammon   | snooker   | mah-jongg  |
| Hobby           | sudoku  | photography | chess    |
| Color   | light-blue   | white     | brown  |
| Movie-Genre           | thriller     | disaster        | comedy |
| Cigar         | dannemann | dunhill   | blend  |
| House     | tower    | victorian     | gothic-revival      |

 